Basic class/prototype pattern using metatables.

```lua
local MyClass = {}
MyClass.__index = MyClass

function MyClass.new(name)
    return setmetatable({ name = name }, MyClass)
end

function MyClass:greet()
    print("Hello, " .. self.name)
end
```

