documentation.value:
Insert element into table.

```lua
local t = {1,2,3}
table.insert(t, 4) -- {1,2,3,4}
table.insert(t, 1, 0) -- {0,1,2,3,4}
```

Remove element from table.

```lua
local t = {1,2,3}
local v = table.remove(t, 2) -- v=2, t={1,3}
table.remove(t) -- removes last
```

Sort table in-place.

```lua
local t = {3,1,2}
table.sort(t) -- {1,2,3}
table.sort(t, function(a,b) return a > b end) -- {3,2,1}
```

Move elements between tables (5.3+).

```lua
local src = {1,2,3,4,5}
local dst = {}
table.move(src, 2, 4, 1, dst) -- dst = {2,3,4}
```

